## Ingredients

- 2 lbs. of Brown Sugar
- 5 Cups of Liquid Butter
- 2 TBSP. Cinnamon

## Instructions

 1. Pour the ingredients into 1/3 black lexan pan and mix well with a hand mixer.

**In general, sauce should be the thickness of pizza sauce.**
